descriptions: Get all services. The services endpoint returns the list of all of the services that the Watson IoT Platform can connect to. The list can include a mixture of services that are either bound or unbound where: Bound services are services that the Watson IoT Platform has been configured to connect to. This can include other services in the same Bluemix space as the Watson IoT Platform or external services. Unbound services are other services in the same Bluemix space as the Watson IoT Platform service that the platform has not yet been configured to connect to. The Watson IoT Platform Dashboard UI must be used to bind to these services.
